summary: This mod adds Water Elves, which can naturally breathe underwater, have night vision, are resistant to cold and shock, but weak to fire. Water Elves can use powerful forms of Shock Magic and Ice Magic.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds Water Elves, which can naturally breathe underwater, have night vision, are resistant to cold and shock, but weak to fire. Water Elves can use powerful forms of Shock Magic and Ice Magic.

There is a Water Elf follower in Riverwood. She has a powerful dagger called "The Aquatic Dagger" that can only be wielded by a Water Elf.

You can also find this mod on the Steam Workshop!!

If anyone has a suggestion, don't hesitate to leave it in the comments!!!
author: Bable631
